Package: KernelTest
Title: Kernel-Based Tests for Differential Histone Enrichment in ChIP-seq
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Tengfei", "Cui", , "tfcui2025@tamu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for detecting differential histone enrichment between case
    and control groups from ChIP-seq profiles. Methods rely on kernel-based
    smoothing and nonparametric statistics to identify differential binding
    regions without restrictive parametric assumptions.
